Package: blockr.otel
Title: OpenTelemetry Profiling Tools for Blockr
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Cynkra", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "mail@cynkra.com")
Description: Provides blockr blocks for profiling Shiny applications with
    OpenTelemetry. Includes an orchestrator block that manages
    otel-desktop-viewer and shinytest2 app drivers, and integrates with
    blockr.echarts for interactive timeline visualization.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Imports:
